    "description": "# Tickr Event Ticketing Platform API\n\nComplete API collection for the Tickr event ticketing platform.\n\n## Base URL\n- **Local Development**: `http://localhost:3000/api`\n- **Staging**: `https://staging.tickr.com/api`\n- **Production**: `https://api.tickr.com/api`\n\n## Authentication\nMost endpoints require JWT Bearer authentication. Use the Login endpoint to obtain tokens.\n\n## Getting Started\n1. Register a new user\n2. Login to get access token\n3. Use the access token in Authorization header for protected endpoints",
